c-Forum for solutions of this challenge." /><span>Solutions</span></a></td><td class="done">done&nbsp;<a href="/challengestats.php?challengeid=341" title="715 users have solved this challenge so far.">[715]</a></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></div><div class="challenge_div">You have 0 0 0 0 0 (that's 5 zeros) and by use of any arithmatic operations available to you on a standard keyboard, without any operands (for example, you can add a '+' but you cant add a '+5') make the equation equal to 120 (only putting them on the left side of course, no trigonometry).
<div class="challenge_1" style="text-align:center;">
ex: 0 + 0 - 0 * 0 % 0 = 120
</div>
Again, the same rules, but now with only 4 0's
<div class="challenge_1" style="text-align:center;">
ex: 0 0 0 0 = 120
</div>
Remove all spaces, and enter the solution like this:
<div class="challenge_1" style="text-align:center;">
solution1_solution2
</div>
Entering the solution is a bit strict, so if you really think you have a correct solution, please <a class="challenge_1" href="/forum/forum_newtopic.php?forumid=50&amp;challenge=341">post it here!</a>
